 This current project investigates the applicability and effectiveness of the CRAFT model as a tool for supporting the CSOs of problem gamblers.

 A comparative analysis will be completed with random assignment of 60 CSOs to either of Group A (CRAFT) or Group B (treatment as usual).

 Twelve individual treatment sessions will be offered to each of the CSOs.

